data.description: Tastefully appointed home in Fort Nugent Highlands neighborhood offers space for everyone.  4 bedrooms, 2 living rooms + bonus room, and 3 car garage just name a few of the features. Enjoy neighborhood visitors from covered from porch. Inside the main level boasts a spacious kitchen, walk-in pantry, living room, family room (w/fireplace) and dining area. Upstairs find private primary suite, 3 additional bedrooms, another full bathroom, and bonus space. Fully-fenced backyard w/oversized deck is great for entertaining. To the side find a dbl gate with parking pad for your RV, boat, or other toys. 3 car garage & large driveway offer an abundance of parking spaces. Within walking distance of fort nugent park.
